data.description: This immaculate 5 bedrooms, 3 baths,2 story home is ready to be occupied by a family that can use an extra bedroom, office space, mancave or woman cave. The master bath and closet are larger than average. The floor plan flows comfortably from room to room. Once you walk in you won't want to leave. The home is conveniently located close to the airport, downtown, and the River City Mall. This is a must see and must have once you've seen it.
